{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"56df3c8337","title":"不断提高劳动生产率","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d3d4d81c3d","index":0,"year":1959,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"56df3c8337"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","name":"红旗一九五九年第九期","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"《红旗》杂志编辑部","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives2/main/43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"1de7680668","name":"柯庆施"}]},"publication_details":{"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"837e2f87fd","type":"paragraph","text":"不断提高劳动生产率","index":0,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"7db7d6f402","type":"paragraph","text":"党的几届六中全会指出：我的国家将经历十五年、二十","index":1,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"156ee0f4cd","type":"paragraph","text":"年或者更多一些时间，建成为具有高度发展药代工业、现代农业、要代科学文化的社会主义国家。在六中全会之后，我例常常盘算这个面题：从现在开始，在完成这个伟大历史任务的斗争中，上海的奋斗目标应是：鼓足最大的干劲，用最少的人力、物力、财力和最快的速度，生产数量更多和量更好的产品，积果更多的建设赛金，送更多的技术力量，来支援全国各地。当然，首先是尽最大的努方完成国家今年交给上海的任务，保证一九五九年国民鑫济计划的胜利实税","index":2,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"abafa1c6cd","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五八年上海工业总产值为一百七十一亿三子万元，比上年增长百分之五十点三（不包括郊区十一个县的工业产值）比一九五二年增长百分之一百八十五点八，比一九四九年增长百分之四百五十三点五。这一年增加的产值为五十七亿三千万元，超过了第一个五年计划期周上海工业产值培加的数字。根据国家今年分配输上海的各项任务，今年上海工业总产值计划为二百四十八亿元，比大跃进的一九五八年增长百分之四十五。完成国家计划是上海人民的最高利签，也是上海人民应尽的青任。我不但要保证完成国家分配的任务，而且要等取超额完成人用什么方法完成呢？我们确定在全面开展增产节豹的群众运动和基本上做到不增加工人的基础上，不断地提高工业劳动生产率。这就要使今年上海工业劳动生产率增长百分之四十五，也就是，要使上海今年一个工人生产的产，相当于去年的一个半工人生产的产值。我们为，不断提高劳效生产率，不但是今年发展上海工业生产、实现大跃进的主要途","index":3,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"150c6456ce","type":"paragraph","text":"径，而且是今后高速度地发展上海工业生产的主要途径。具","index":4,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"d77ef645bb","type":"paragraph","text":"有这样，在完成我国建成社会主义的伟大的历史任务中，上柯庆","index":5,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"44ee776ddf","type":"paragraph","text":"海才能更好地发挥它应有的作用。","index":6,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"05fc5a80a1","type":"paragraph","text":"不断提高劳动生产率是发展施上海工业的主要途径经呢？能不能办到晚？","index":7,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"a2431c49ce","type":"paragraph","text":"在上海工作的同志中，对于发展上海工业生产，主要采取增加工人，还是主要依靠提商劳动生产事，是存在着不同的看法的。一部分同志偏重子增加工人；但是大多数同志觉得，就上海实际情况来看，应蔽以不断提高工业劳动生产率为主。","index":8,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"e902dbe9e8","type":"paragraph","text":"增加工人是发展工业生产的途径之一。在我国大亿人口中，终村人口点总人口百分之八十以上，这是我国经济落后的标志。所以，我们的国家今后必须兴办静多大型工业企业和中小型工业企业藏藏扩充和壮大工人阶极队伍。这在全国来歌，是完全正磺的。但是，就上海这个老工业基地来，由于它地处沿海，距离原料、燃料产地和内地市场过远，为着工业布局合理和政变滑海与内地解济发展的不平衡状态，上海新建、扩建项目不宜过多。增加工人也很有限。因此，增加工人不应当","index":9,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"c54cc0f652","type":"paragraph","text":"例一：下面所举的营第二印染厂，一九五八年的职工人数，比一九五七年减少了将近百分之四，但是产植和净产植反而都增加了百分之三十以上。","index":10,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"e5da885b94","type":"paragraph","text":"职工人数网堂","index":11,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"bc6a3834f4","type":"paragraph","text":"宝九","index":12,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"69078599c7","type":"paragraph","text":"玩第","index":13,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"17362d48e8","type":"paragraph","text":"年","index":14,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"eb2715642c","type":"paragraph","text":"1142印","index":15,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"8ae378358b","type":"paragraph","text":"五八","index":16,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"977df9901f","type":"paragraph","text":"1.100九","index":17,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"265f8d39fc","type":"paragraph","text":"年","index":18,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"440e9b8349","type":"paragraph","text":"（注）染","index":19,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"3de8e0fd55","type":"paragraph","text":"九五八年和一九五七厂","index":20,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"f93f3379f1","type":"paragraph","text":"8-0898","index":21,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"90938c2f08","type":"paragraph","text":"年培减的百分出（注）一九五八年还抽调出部分人用以建立化工车称汽车修理车限成为今后发展上海工业生产的主要途径","index":22,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"7aab83b1e1","type":"paragraph","text":"不断提高工业劳动生产率也是发展工业生产的途径。对发展全国工业生产来款是如此：上海工业生产的发展，无其必须朵取不断提高劳动生产率为主要途径。老动生产率的高低，是由所生产的产品数量和所消耗的劳动时间的对比来计算的。生产同样数量的产品，但却节省更多数量的劳动时周；或者是消耗同样数量的劳动时间但却生产更多数量的产品，这都叫劳动生产率的提高。一个工厂增加一个工人，只能增加一双手，或者是八个劳动小时。如果不断提高劳动生产率，由于单位产品所器要的劳动时调的节省，虽然这个工厂没有绝加一个工人，但也无异于增加了一只手、一双手。更多双手，或者是四个劳动小时、八个劳动小时、更多个劳动小时。这样，秘使减少了-部分工人，总产值也不会减少，或者还可以增加。我们举儿个例子来酚明产","index":23,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"1a34748836","type":"paragraph","text":"值（元）","index":24,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"9fe129a0e9","type":"paragraph","text":"净产值（元）（每一职工平均）","index":25,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"430a12fd62","type":"paragraph","text":"（每一职工车均）52,830","index":26,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"205bd134b0","type":"paragraph","text":"8.82E70.245","index":27,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"6eb124bdec","type":"paragraph","text":"12.065+342%","index":28,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"b0d06e1f28","type":"paragraph","text":"+86-71%","index":29,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"3b986a18ea","type":"paragraph","text":"例二，下面是去午十二月上海铁--厂和三厂的三个炼纲率的H较。上三厂老转城中国的劳动生产率最高，这个车平均每一职工的产量几平比上细-广新转车商多一传。","index":30,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"fdb41d65e7","type":"paragraph","text":"车间本月","index":31,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"f16be48c39","type":"paragraph","text":"花产室","index":32,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"8bf023dcce","type":"paragraph","text":"尚","index":33,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"c733aa2c15","type":"paragraph","text":"校备（座）","index":34,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"a7ea543c72","type":"paragraph","text":"（吨）","index":35,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"264d6bf367","type":"paragraph","text":"诚性8吨6座上一厂新翰烤","index":36,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"27680a9ab1","type":"paragraph","text":"20.683上三厂老转","index":37,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"330cfd2945","type":"paragraph","text":"诚性6吨生座","index":38,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"9dddd3be4c","type":"paragraph","text":"27178上端三厂新灶","index":39,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"91fd68dcb9","type":"paragraph","text":"诚性8吨6座","index":40,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"e0682c0918","type":"paragraph","text":"29408根据上海治金局一九五八年十二月统计资料","index":41,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"864acf7c06","type":"paragraph","text":"例三：去年上海某柴主要行业，由子单位产品所需要的劳动时间的节有，每一个工入平均产量提高多。如下表，","index":42,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"33b65b7b8f","type":"paragraph","text":"汽车翰胎电","index":43,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"5ed278fe74","type":"paragraph","text":"力（万度）","index":44,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"4e209ae254","type":"paragraph","text":"（条）","index":45,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"b380f7045b","type":"paragraph","text":"50.1","index":46,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"9ab56a26d3","type":"paragraph","text":"197","index":47,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"3b358943f4","type":"paragraph","text":"九五七年每年","index":48,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"7cae53db02","type":"paragraph","text":"79","index":49,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"1fb5d56cf1","type":"paragraph","text":"80G","index":50,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"c70c269a3b","type":"paragraph","text":"九五几年九五八年鞍","index":51,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"4890643d9a","type":"paragraph","text":"38-67%一九五七年增","index":52,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"5258ee30a3","type":"paragraph","text":"56·83%","index":53,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"c36f7a5e1c","type":"paragraph","text":"长的百分比","index":54,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"cf59681a82","type":"paragraph","text":"从前面所举的例子来看：劳动生产率意高，意味着单位劳动时周内所生产的工业产品量意多，也就是，用以扩大再生产的生产登料和用以满足人民生活需要的生活资料慈多；阅时，也意味着活劳动物化劳动（原料、燃料、机器折旧费用）您加节省，单位产品的成本感加降饭，也就是，用以扩大再生产的积果基金有可能您来意多，生活奇科的份格也有可能随之相应降低。南此可见，在社会主义制度下，不断提商劳动生产率，是增加社会物衡财富、扩大再生产和提高人民福利的源泉。进一步看，在社会主义制度下，不断","index":55,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"1540221588","type":"paragraph","text":"劳动生产率（实物）","index":56,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"ba1eb13edb","type":"paragraph","text":"车周本月","index":57,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"34bc34182c","type":"paragraph","text":"每人每月","index":58,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"8cf97b1acc","type":"paragraph","text":"吃","index":59,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"f467f950c0","type":"paragraph","text":"拆职工总人数","index":60,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"c3ba6c5cb9","type":"paragraph","text":"天","index":61,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"c3c6f7d9e0","type":"paragraph","text":"T数（吨）","index":62,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"584e1968b7","type":"paragraph","text":"8-272.181","index":63,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91de5e48","articleId":"56df3c8337"},{"id":"0887b2de46","type":"paragraph","text":"9.481488","index":64,"publicationId":"43b19feb-ef2c-4abb-b73f-decc91